(Tasks Module Flow) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Permissions) Tj
T*
(- view_tasks: own task dashboard, my tasks, notifications.) Tj
T*
(- view_team_tasks: task list, kanban, calendar, team task dashboard.) Tj
T*
(- create_task: create task workflow.) Tj
T*
(- edit_task: update task details/status.) Tj
T*
(- delete_task: delete tasks.) Tj
T*
(- assign_task: assign tasks and see team task workflows.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Assignment workflow) Tj
T*
(1. Admin/manager/HR with create_task or assign_task opens Tasks.) Tj
T*
(2. Create Task loads active employees from /api/tasks/members/.) Tj
T*
(3. Assigner selects employee, priority, due date, related module, and saves.) Tj
T*
(4. Backend stores task with assigned_by and assigned_to.) Tj
T*
(5. Assigned employee with view_tasks sees it in own task dashboard/my tasks.) Tj
T*
(6. Team users with view_team_tasks or assign_task see all tenant tasks.) Tj
T*
(7. Comments, status changes, archive, and notifications are saved through backend APIs.) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
endobj
