stream
BT
/F1 11 Tf
50 780 Td
14 TL
(Leads and Follow Ups Flow) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Permissions) Tj
T*
(- view_leads: see assigned leads or all leads if also assign_lead/view_lead_analytics.) Tj
T*
(- create_lead: add lead.) Tj
T*
(- edit_lead: edit lead.) Tj
T*
(- delete_lead: delete lead.) Tj
T*
(- assign_lead: assign counselors and view broader lead pool.) Tj
T*
(- view_followups: see follow-up records.) Tj
T*
(- create_followup: log lead conversations and reminders.) Tj
T*
(- manage_lead_forms: form builder.) Tj
T*
(- view_lead_analytics: analytics dashboard.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Lead workflow) Tj
T*
(1. User with create_lead adds a lead using active intake form.) Tj
T*
(2. If user lacks assign_lead, backend assigns the lead to that user.) Tj
T*
(3. User with view_leads sees only allowed leads.) Tj
T*
(4. User with create_followup logs conversation from Lead Details.) Tj
T*
(5. Follow Ups page shows pending/completed follow-up actions.) Tj
T*
(6. Analytics is visible only with view_lead_analytics.) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
endobj
