50 780 Td
14 TL
(Revenue and Affiliate Flow) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Revenue permissions) Tj
T*
(- view_revenue: open Revenue dashboard.) Tj
T*
(- manage_revenue: future management workflow access.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Revenue workflow) Tj
T*
(1. Revenue dashboard calls /api/revenue/overview/.) Tj
T*
(2. Backend checks view_revenue.) Tj
T*
(3. Revenue is calculated from lead fields named Revenue, Fee, Course Fee, or Amount.) Tj
T*
(4. Admission Confirmed leads count as confirmed revenue.) Tj
T*
(5. Interested and Follow-Up Pending leads count as pipeline revenue.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Affiliate permissions) Tj
T*
(- view_affiliate: open affiliate dashboard workflows.) Tj
T*
(- manage_affiliate: manage affiliate workflows.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Affiliate workflow) Tj
T*
(1. Sidebar shows Affiliate only when permission is granted.) Tj
T*
(2. Affiliate backend endpoints require view_affiliate or manage_affiliate.) Tj
T*
(3. Public affiliate/customer registration remains public.) Tj
T*
(4. Dashboard, referrals, commissions, payments, profile, and notifications are permission-pr) Tj
T*
(otected.) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
