(Operational Checklist) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(After code update) Tj
T*
(1. Run backend migrations.) Tj
T*
(   python manage.py migrate) Tj
T*
(2. Seed permissions.) Tj
T*
(   python manage.py seed_permissions) Tj
T*
(3. Restart backend server.) Tj
T*
(4. Restart frontend dev server if needed.) Tj
T*
(5. Login as admin or superadmin.) Tj
T*
(6. Open Permission Manager.) Tj
T*
(7. Grant employee permissions by module.) Tj
T*
(8. Logout/login as employee to refresh token permissions.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Expected examples) Tj
T*
(- Employee with view_tasks only: sees Tasks, Dashboard, My Tasks, Notifications.) Tj
T*
(- Employee with create_task only: sees Create Task only.) Tj
T*
(- Counselor with view_leads and create_followup: sees leads and follow-ups they are allowed ) Tj
T*
(to access.) Tj
T*
(- Revenue user with view_revenue: sees Revenue dashboard without needing view_leads.) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
